  "3231040": {
    "name": "语默行间",
    "steam_appid": 3231040,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>教学楼外攀缘的爬藤，</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>电风扇下漫卷的书本。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>课桌板内翻飞的拇指，</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>九宫格上跃动的青春。</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>那样腾空的日子在十几年前就已经结束了，但时间真的能带走一切吗？</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《语默行间》这款独特的文字冒险游戏，你终于得以重温学生时代。操作老款手机，查收短信，<strong>逐句选择回复内容</strong>，在九键之间铺展独属于你的青涩流年。没有社交媒体的纷扰，没有成人世界的烦恼，置身于那伴着虫鸣的懵懂夏夜，聆听按下发送键时的心跳……而回到当下，你将面对一场与故人们的全新相遇，并对这段回忆作出最终诠释。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >忠实还原功能机时代的手机界面，融入天气与环境音效，带你重回那个节奏舒缓的美好年代。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/c533374de6269a898240a6b62f3d7f66.poster.avif?t=1771314360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/c533374de6269a898240a6b62f3d7f66.webm?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/c533374de6269a898240a6b62f3d7f66.mp4?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >于 2006 年的初中启程，到 2010 年的高中，再到 2014 年的大学。若这恰巧也是你的青春轨迹，那你会因熟悉的时代印记而会心一笑；即便不是，你也能在这段旅程找到自己的青春共鸣。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/786f00aad5d5febc4286315e2d78ecc4.poster.avif?t=1771314360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/786f00aad5d5febc4286315e2d78ecc4.webm?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/786f00aad5d5febc4286315e2d78ecc4.mp4?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >用短信与手机那一端的同学们交流，并<strong>推进一段若即若离、难以名状的关系</strong>。对着那条信息的字里行间看了好久——你在过度解读吗？你不在过度解读吗？编辑信息时<strong>字斟句酌</strong>——你在瞻前顾后吗？你在故作洒脱吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/38e5d05b9496485df0598c733dfcfaba.poster.avif?t=1771314360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/38e5d05b9496485df0598c733dfcfaba.webm?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/38e5d05b9496485df0598c733dfcfaba.mp4?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>逐句选择回复内容，见证你的选择以各种方式催化故事分岔，影响当下，塑造未来。</strong>这里没有旁白，你是唯一的主角。<strong>每个分支都受到尊重，没有虚假选项和死路，也没有惩罚和失败。</strong>轻松地按照自己的意愿和节奏游玩，游戏关闭时也不会推进时间。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/22fddb8ab4ad512be2940405415ee721.poster.avif?t=1771314360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/22fddb8ab4ad512be2940405415ee721.webm?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/22fddb8ab4ad512be2940405415ee721.mp4?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在课间的喧闹之外，偶尔探索校园的 B 面。你相信那些被<span class=\"bb_strike\">添油加醋</span>流传了一届又一届的轶事吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/61ebadc955f8eac0e825943cf46e817a.poster.avif?t=1771314360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/61ebadc955f8eac0e825943cf46e817a.webm?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/61ebadc955f8eac0e825943cf46e817a.mp4?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >别忘了，你掌握着来自“未来”的知识。是否要向伙伴们透露一些？看他们会一笑置之，将信将疑，还是……把你当作神仙？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/8f74ffddd0bd1bc6dff4190bf4bfda5a.poster.avif?t=1771314360\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/8f74ffddd0bd1bc6dff4190bf4bfda5a.webm?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/8f74ffddd0bd1bc6dff4190bf4bfda5a.mp4?t=1771314360\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >直观、流畅的选择与输入系统——无论键盘鼠标，都能轻松高效地浏览选项并完成输入。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>或许你会发现一些秘密，或许不会</strong>，又或许，在屏幕上游走的除了闪烁的光标，也有你从一开始就在回避的真相？不过请放心，就像生活一样，这个故事里的一切都没有标准答案，尽管用<i>你</i>喜欢的方式去体验和解读。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在数小时内完成一个周目，而<strong>多周目的重复内容将被刻意减少</strong>，你能遇见新话题，并有机会解锁由每段只言片语牵引着的<strong>多重结局</strong>。再来一次时，你的选择会改变吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >有一些彩蛋（但没有破坏年代感的网络流行语或烂梗），你能找到吗？</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >所有对话和剧本均为手工编写，而非 AI 生成。</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>你忘了太多事，却始终记得没发出去的那条短信。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>即刻加入愿望单，静候那缕来自青春深处的回音。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras/641203b2bd0fec680da8bd460d30cc55.avif?t=1771314360\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3231040/extras_big/641203b2bd0fec680da8bd460d30cc55.avif?t=1771314360 width=800 height=958 /></span></p>",
